ZH: 他总是大言不惭地说自己多有才华。
EN: He always boasts shamelessly about his talents.
ZH: 她做错事了也从不感到羞愧，大言不惭地辩解起来。
EN: She never feels guilty when she does something wrong, instead shamelessly justifying herself.
ZH: 那个男人对自己过去的业绩大言不惭。
EN: The man shamelessly boasted about his past achievements.
